{"thig2.3:0.1":"Therigatha 2.3 ","thig2.3:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thig2.3:0.3":"Sumangalamatatherigatha ","thig2.3:1.1":"“Sumuttika sumuttika, ","thig2.3:1.2":"Sadhumuttikamhi musalassa; ","thig2.3:1.3":"Ahiriko me chattakam vapi, ","thig2.3:1.4":"Ukkhalika me deddubham vati. ","thig2.3:2.1":"Raganca aham dosanca, ","thig2.3:2.2":"Cicciti ciccititi vihanami; ","thig2.3:2.3":"Sa rukkhamulamupagamma, ","thig2.3:2.4":"Aho sukhanti sukhato jhayami”ti. ","thig2.3:3.1":"… Sumangalamata theri …. "}